{"tid":1609232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣中槍少年險遭射中心臟已取出子彈碎","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T13:45:02.000Z","uid":252013,"like":214,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"9787279040b701d54f440273dfb5c7a6e3d59703","tid":1609232,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:01:46.000Z","msg":"from news<br />\n<br />\n今日（10月1日）全港多區爆發激烈衝突，警方形容多處出現「暴動行為」。下午約4時，在荃灣一名18歲男示威者中實彈後倒地，目前在伊利沙伯醫院心胸外科留醫。消息指，該名少年被射中肺部，幸未傷及心臟、大動脈，但有子彈碎片留在體內，要接駁人工肺呼吸，現時經手術已成功取出子彈。<br />\n早前消息指，他被射中肺部，懷疑有子彈碎片留在體內，需由瑪嘉烈醫院轉送到伊利沙伯醫院心胸外科。據了解，他部分肋骨骨折，而肝臟、心臟及脊椎完好無損，惟由於子彈遺留在他身體的後方導至血胸，即血液流進胸腔和肺部之間的位置，需要接受引流手...<a href=\"https://headline.appt.cf/share.php?a=headlinewwl&amp;id=93167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadline.appt.cf%2Fshare.php%3Fa%3Dheadlinewwl%26id%3D93167&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=6c5bfd27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headline.appt.cf/share.php?a=headlinewwl&amp;id=93167</a>"},{"pid":"a8e5a16a67778530bff9a72a38afea5d0cec6639","tid":1609232,"uid":177082,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:02:29.000Z","msg":"經過今日 殺警都唔係問題 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609207</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2a9b614878c1b6a7650e0761f862ee9e63d52cb2","tid":1609232,"uid":35746,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"不幸中既大幸"},{"pid":"dd622327d68fe9307a9c1fcd55d527d2ca10201a","tid":1609232,"uid":157197,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:02:57.000Z","msg":"香港人會幫你討回公道！"},{"pid":"f38ab4a83d4a466789844f7d36e9a489bf3ba696","tid":1609232,"uid":70183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:03:05.000Z","msg":"god bless"},{"pid":"0023de612598daea137fa4727a5ba7735c513390","tid":1609232,"uid":34444,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T